bilingual.source: He works in the hope of success.

bilingual.target: 他的爱好给他带来了成功。

bilingual.source: I hope David will have great success in the future.
bilingual.target: 我希望大卫将来会取得很大的成功。

bilingual.source: You can never imagine how difficult the road to success is.
bilingual.target: 你永远无法想象成功之路有多艰难。

bilingual.source: With the majority of attempts to climb Qomolangma resulting in success.
bilingual.target: 大多数攀登珠峰的尝试都取得了成功。

bilingual.source: Only one of these invented languages has enjoyed any success, though.
bilingual.target: 然而，这些发明的语言中只有一种成功了。

bilingual.source: She managed to unlock the secret to success.
bilingual.target: 她成功解锁了成功的秘诀。

list.abstract: success（英[səkˈses]，美[səkˈses]），英语单词，名词，译为成功；兴旺；发迹。短语搭配有achieve success（取得成功）。例句为“Education is the key to success.（教育是成功的关键。）” 该单词的同根词有动词为succeed，名词为successor（继承者），形容词为successful，副词为successfully，复数为successes。
株式会社SUCCESS（日语：株式会社サクセス；英语：SUCCESS Corporation），日本游戏开发商和发行商，于1978年6月成立，总部在日本东京。

yingyinNormal.en: It was low probability of success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如此低概率事件尽然成功了。

yingyinNormal.en: Enjoy the taste of success, Riley. It's sweet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 享受成功的滋味吧，莱丽，是甜的哦。

yingyinNormal.en: And because it was dimming his prospects for success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但他向成功的道路却是变得越来越昏暗了。

yingyinNormal.en: What happens next? Oh, more testing, more success, more fame.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那接下来怎么办？更多的实验，更多的成功，当然，还有更多的荣誉。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. So, a success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，所以，成功了。

yingyinNormal.en: Success, real success is being willing to do the things that other people are not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 成功，真正的成功是愿意去做别人都不愿意做的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: Eventually the success of the mission and the well-being of the people alongside me became more important than my own success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比我自己的成功更重要，和我身边人的福祉比我自己的成功更重要。

yingyinNormal.en: I've come to realize that success is not a matter of attaining one's goals. I've found that when I reached each new higher level of success, I rarely remained satisfied.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我意识到成功不是达到目标。每当我达到一个新高度的成功，我很少感到满足。

yingyinNormal.en: And I have to tell you, I became pretty comfortable with that level of success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我得承认，这样的成功让我感觉非常好。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, first of all, the surgery was a success, and secondly, I didn't even want you there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先，手术非常成功，其次，我根本不想要你去。

yingyinNormal.en: Riley's gonna be a success and I'm gonna sponge off her until she gets sick of me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱丽会成为成功人士，我会去抱她大腿，直到她烦我为止。

yingyinNormal.en: Koosh balls? Inside those cans, you will find the key to success in your business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 橡胶毛毛球？在那些桶子里，你们能发现打开生意成功之门的钥匙。

yingyinNormal.en: So let's make sure women earn equal pay for equal work, and have a fair shot at success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，让我们确保妇女能够同工同酬，并在成功上有相同的机会。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm now at a stage in my own life in which it is much more important to me to pass along what I've learned about how to be successful than to seek more success for myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在的生活阶段对我更重要的是，将我所学到的成功的知识传递下去，而不是自己追寻成功。

yingyinNormal.en: At the very least they deserve a Congress that doesn't stand in the way of their success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，国会不应该成为他们去往成功道路上的绊脚石，这是毋庸置疑的。

yingyinNormal.en: So if everyone liked it, and you liked it, that would make this a success. Which would make you. A bitch?
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是大家都喜欢，你也喜欢，那就代表很成功，而你就是，恶婆娘？

yingyinNormal.en: So you're just gonna hide your success from him? I know. Am I terrible? No. I do that, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你就对他隐瞒了你的成功吗？我知道不好。我是不是太坏了？不会啊。我也这么做。

yingyinNormal.en: Whoever threw that is not afraid to really go for it, and that will go a long way toward success in business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 扔球过来的那个人从心所愿，放胆去做能在商业道路上获得更长远的成功。

yingyinNormal.en: You expect much success with that, Harold? So desperate to find Shaw, you're willing to say anything to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你认为这样做能成功吗，哈罗德？你不顾一切想找到肖，什么瞎话都愿意编。

yingyinNormal.en: Work hard? Play by the rules? You aren't guaranteed success. Your children will not have a better life than you did.
yingyinNormal.zh: 努力工作，遵守规则，不保证你们能成功，你们孩子的生活不会比你们好。

examination_example.sentence: In short, <highlight>success</highlight> in creating AI could be the biggest event in the history of our civilisation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 简而言之，成功创建 AI 可能是我们文明的历史上最大的事件。

examination_example.sentence: Maybe you see low customer participation at first, or conversely, so much <highlight>success</highlight> that the cost of recycling becomes too high.

examination_example.sentence: With this study, researchers examined early academic attention and emotionalize skills and how each contributed to academic <highlight>success</highlight> into young adulthood.

word_usage.usage:
success表“成功”时，为抽象不可数名词。“...的成功”可用the success of表达。
示例：Confidence is the key to success.
信心是成功的关键。

success表“成功的人/事物的”时，为可数名词。
示例：The party was a big success. 
这次聚会非常成功。

examination_example.sentence: Other factors may also significantly influence a project's <highlight>success</highlight>, most notably, the size of a scientist's personal and professional networks, and how much a researcher promotes a project on their own.
